==English==

=== Noun ===

# {{physics}} the [[fundamental force]] of [[attraction]] that exists between all [[particle]]s with [[mass]] in the [[universe]].  It is the [[weakest]] of the four forces, and possesses a [[gauge boson]] known as the [[graviton]].  See also [[gravity]].

